Package swingtree.style

Class SvgIcon

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.ImageIcon
      • swingtree.style.SvgIcon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.Icon
    public final class SvgIcon
extends javax.swing.ImageIcon
    A specialized ImageIcon subclass that allows you to use SVG based icon images in your UI. This in essence just a wrapper around the JSVG library, which renders SVG images into Java2D graphics API.
